These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, ambient, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, italian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, bike, boat
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the pakistani and the fan of country##2
3. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the italian is on the right of the fan of blues##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country    | ambient      | blues      | pop    |
| Nationality   | dutch | canadian | pakistani | italian |
| Transport     | roller    | boat       | bike     | jet-ski     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, peas, potato, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, baking, collecting, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, horror, fantasy
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating peas##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating peas##1
7. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | banana     | zucchini     | peas       | potato    |
| Hobby         | baking | collecting   | gardening | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | horror | documentary    | martial-arts        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, juice, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, german, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, rugby, weightlifting
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the german##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the french##3
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the german is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | iced-tea  | juice    | cola |
| Nationality   | german   | italian  | french  | chinese    |
| Sport         | soccer    | weightlifting | skiing | rugby  |

