.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, apple, cauliflower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, western, thriller, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, cat, horse
1. the owner of the pony is between the person watching western movies and the person eating carrot##2
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the fish is the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | apple   | carrot     | mango | cauliflower |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | fantasy | zombie   | western     |
| Pet           | horse | cat      | pony     | fish       |

