.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, banana, carrot, plum
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, freelancer, journalist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, fantasy, thriller
1. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
3. the freelancer is the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the dancer is between the person eating carrot and the person eating banana##2
5. the freelancer is on the right of the journalist##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating plum##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
8. the person eating carrot is the person watching fantasy movies##1
9. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | carrot      | plum | banana      | pear |
| Job           | engineer | dancer | journalist | freelancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | satire     | comedy   |

