.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant, electrician, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, soul, blues, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, climbing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is parkour is the freelancer##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the fan of r&b##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
5. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
6. the electrician is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the accountant is on the right of the fan of folk##1
8. the accountant is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | freelancer    | accountant   | electrician | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | blues   | r&b         | soul        |
| Sport         | parkour | surfing | climbing         | cycling       |

