.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, photography, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, electrician, pilot, dressmaker
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 4. the pilot is on the right of the indonesian##1
 5. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the electrician is on the left or right of the pilot##3
11. the electrician is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | photography    | magic-tricks  | collecting | woodworking   |
| Job           | dressmaker | electrician   | pilot    | freelancer |
| Nationality   | polish      | indonesian | colombian | canadian  |

