.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, potato, lemon, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, singing, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, time-travel, documentary, family
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
2. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating potato##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | lemon | potato    | orange | onion    |
| Hobby         | singing     | photography | drawing  | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | family      | animation   | documentary         |

