3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fisherman is on the right of the police-officer##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | cola            | almond-milk     | juice      |
| Job           | electrician    | police-officer | fisherman     | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie    | thriller | sports    |

