3. the person driving the car is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
6. the person driving the car is between the person driving the motorbike and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the dressmaker##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | almond-milk   | water   | tea    | cola |
| Job         | dressmaker | lawyer    | architect      | analyst |
| Transport   | motorbike      | car | bus | trike   |

