3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate      | lemonade | cola       | juice  |
| Hobby       | baking | rock-climbing | hiking    | camping |
| Transport   | helicopter     | tram         | skateboard | bike     |

