4. the owner of the dog is between the coach and the italian##2
5. the coach is the british##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the british##3
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the librarian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
