.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing, woodworking, filmmaking
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bus, train, boat
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the train##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | sprite    | 7up      | iced-tea |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks  | singing | filmmaking | woodworking     |
| Transport   | roller | bus        | train  | boat        |

