.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, cherry, potato
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, project-manager, software-developer, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing, rugby, lacrosse
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating cherry##2
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the software-developer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cherry | grapes  | eggplant  | potato           |
| Job     | firefighter | software-developer | project-manager   | lawyer |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | skiing       | ice-hockey | rugby  |

 